Subject: [R-es] Operaciones con Arrays...creo.
In-Reply-To: <CA+8ueybNw-_hwNoprCGhn2d1PWX5A1qxysfaEx9x=oikWeHf7Q@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CA+8ueya=b6r7hM6x1Qm_VUfUh8Aq97RCNod8VPQr-Zs2vrpV=g@mail.gmail.com>
 <CAHo_aET-FOoukdskS_qTNtqEZZwSPqtYR6mU9p0hMjq2hw74jA@mail.gmail.com>
